-9fe9-2736e5fd4320\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-40aeac5d-3886-4da5-9cf2-e819946402b0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">디지털 인쇄의 발달로 인해</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-537a5137-bed7-45eb-a0fb-77ab201fa133\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-f51174ea-8c54-4f03-bac3-ffd9447f8ac6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">소량 다품종 생산이</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-064b7e02-603e-4181-b82e-9add71c9a568\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-d97d56c3-363f-4e28-b3b6-68a532fdc7d5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">가능해졌습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-5615ba47-c2aa-4a7c-bc24-e67c4b81f871\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e973124c-02f0-403a-a42c-68aa21c9207f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-07fb6f21-9f49-47d2-aa9a-a43b35a00aae\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8bc993ed-194f-4227-98a2-b96b3bc69cf2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">다품종 생산 품목도 다양해지고</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-d6879930-a197-437f-ad54-5adafe0693bb\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-1713e77e-df84-4399-81ae-bd3435109d63\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이제는 스티커도 소량으로 주문이</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-d0e4042c-5c32-4052-b33b-70eac5a8242f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-95b4567e-f958-4a07-8d28-9ef47da07ce7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">가능합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-19847d86-8996-4484-ae0f-bf66115378c6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-2ca9ecf4-c5d1-402a-8836-0694d4e1c295\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-56b145ac-8fd0-4d68-bf30-d03721811dac\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-71479e85-afdf-433f-a1b4-8ee521cb2aa0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-64fda013-5c56-4c22-81b6-4d70b370ff60\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4458e972-6cac-4c86-87dd-0a581408103d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-1fc15f19-f9c8-4e11-b558-11c1e092ca78\" style=\"\">반칼/완칼</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3408f83c-25dc-4844-9d63-8901b3c8b5ee\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-8763cb08-727e-4085-960a-023dba967a83\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ef79fca3-e83b-4815-be2c-70890d1b981a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">스티커는 반칼스티커와 완칼스티커로 나뉩니다. 일단 인쇄를 잘 모르시는 고객님이 너무 많아 설명드려 보겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-b0e00eb8-9736-4c12-84ac-8800652a9b72\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-2d666540-06a3-4dec-a785-6bef943216bc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-f84a343f-c826-4ce4-84f2-396b2ff8678b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b768c7e7-35a3-4fc6-a17d-352106ad25f4\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>반칼스티커</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-631fd058-0bde-4ffc-b62d-b6ba8bcfdd20\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-0f60014d-4a7d-43d2-9534-32d77c2f31f9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">반칼스티커는 모든 스티커의 기본인 방식입니다. 반칼은 앞에서 스티커를 뜯을 수 있도록 반만 칼집을 내서 제작됩니다. 후지에도 보통은 반칼이 들어가지만 디지털 소량 인쇄에서는 후지반칼은 없다고 보시면 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-e1712787-bf5a-4b12-9a06-e8d8a901303b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-7f9d7b1b-854e-467c-aa97-1b1e37b4f490\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-99a60bf9-ed83-4518-8180-d392251bce54\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-9dcf2ea8-aa48-4a94-90c3-d289915cbc59\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하지만 오프셋으로 진행되는 자유형 도무송의 대량 발주는 후면에 기본적으로 반칼이 삽입되어 진행되므로 이 다른 점을 숙지해 주세요. 이로 인해 앞면에 반칼자국이 발생되는데 이는 대부분의 업체에서 사고처리로 인정하지 않습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2ac0f280-7fed-49b8-9655-855b5202134a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223888263832/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f6672fa7-1320-4690-b9fd-ebbfd2b2c6a6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-bc7b0396-7d43-43d1-b3ea-a0e1435ac6ff\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-26422e33-cee6-40b8-aef2-d7bb411d013b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">앞에서 칼이 반만 들어가 있어서 뜯을 수 있는 스티커가 반칼 스티커입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-19b352a8-4b77-41e4-8bd7-9d1264874de7\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e4c89bdc-26a8-4ab7-9fd4-6f2a48cba04e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-23e5adfa-1b20-43d7-82e5-77560795eb54\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-7f39ba3e-b149-4adb-898c-f70934420c82\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-4dd14abf-db55-4bfd-aced-61f6d88e292d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-2bf3369f-7403-4c61-9b26-6eac75a54932\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-c323f2be-e1ce-467a-a99d-2be900c54164\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-841a3255-ff80-4692-a85f-7cea1eedc84d\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>완칼스티커</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-b137bcb4-db69-4e42-93e3-0d6eb4453433\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-a54b3aa5-79ee-43bd-a792-2e66676d0f54\" style=\"color:#555555;\">완칼스티커는 모양 자체를 완전히 커팅하는 방식입니다. 디지털 커팅 칼날이 정해진 모양을 완전하게 커팅해서 만들어서 뜯을 때 끝부분을 분리해서 뜯어내고 정해진 모양 그대로 납품이 이루어집니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3df6ee76-4c3a-47b8-9edb-0f048223424b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223888263832/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ecc0c397-f492-40df-b487-d6b824d32db0\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-ffbb752c-0eab-42bc-87f5-a774873ae59d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-92e1cfb3-4a7b-4971-b32d-6c6b682bd7ed\" style=\"color:#555555;\">다만 완칼 스티커는 정교하기는 하지만 뜯을 때 뒷면 후지에 반칼이 없음으로 불편함이 발생될 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-12c1d012-572d-4b37-a652-609354a093e9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-7bfdd493-163b-49d5-912a-6077ab381b8d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-c28b8255-7379-4f96-89f8-a527f9853ba4\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-98614f83-6f40-4a84-923f-6db45cd26e9a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">반칼과 완칼이 크게 다른 것은 반칼의 경우 여러 장을 한 대지에 만들어 작업할 수 있지만 완칼은 하나하나를 따로 뜯어서 작업되어 조각조각이 난다는 뜻입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f93d14f9-1dc2-4e0e-8fb8-6b474965c99c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\" style=\"max-width:512px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223888263832/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9e7521fb-aee3-4746-93e5-07d768ba74bb\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-607d53f9-7c8c-45a8-9b6f-d184eb042276\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-fe86363f-1d1a-46c7-9df9-edb1c3a29ec2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">A4에 6개의 각자 스티커를 조판하여 뜯을 수 있도록 작업했습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-62364405-e9f2-403e-9751-0734327daaf4\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e0c74fc2-f2c9-44dc-b506-89c263085b88\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-67e931ce-1ae5-4482-bd1b-123cbb9688d0\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7a5d72e3-841d-4de0-8a07-7973992c538a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-c1cbf6d2-93a2-4a89-a0c4-2cd3eab93e2e\" style=\"\">작업 일지</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9ba1b3c4-7de7-43ef-815d-64a5e92ce3b3\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\" style=\"max-width:639px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223888263832/006.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-cd10530f-22ec-463c-82e0-b72cba027376\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-260d296a-4694-4b5d-89f8-a92da7c14ae3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-33767814-76c1-4a91-bf17-b62823c8b90d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">신송식품에서 해외 전시회 목적으로 소량 스티커 제작 의뢰가 들어왔습니다. 물론 급한 인쇄물이라 저희는 최대한 빠르게 견적과 디자인 검증에 임했습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a46b6706-c4f1-43c8-91d0-2a0757504169\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\" style=\"max-width:621px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223888263832/007.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-00ad41db-f1f5-4c6e-be5d-1e5c5b1702b9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-96bd53bf-016f-4b99-9613-39110cb0a90a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-aa249273-2570-4def-8785-22a74ad98048\" style=\"color:#555555;\">디자인 자료를 받기 전에 일단 견적을 제출하기 위해 대략적인 사이즈와 수량을 요청드려 파악했습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-3d3f2120-1920-4846-9d08-bbcdd2c61500\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-c579babd-d4cf-40cf-86fc-1f01c77fe5c6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-4732b4cb-3406-4f49-8e87-af397bc37b56\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-a8c6942c-df9d-4dc4-9f78-cee4a074da26\" style=\"color:#555555;\">기본 아트지 백색 90g의 스티커 용지와 단면 CMYK 4도 인쇄, 그리고 유광 코팅으로 견적이 이루어져 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-b793aaf7-596d-479f-b74a-4e11604ac7f3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ffbddcff-d8a1-44a8-ac6b-1b6e2ac87d1e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-727a7a67-ddd8-4e2d-87b0-c357dfdb1937\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e1b47689-b083-4afd-96a8-c33e9aa983da\" style=\"color:#555555;\">각 수량은 페이지당 8장입니다. 극 소량이나 최대한 합리적인 단가로 견적을 제출했습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-c278197a-01f1-4f73-ad01-13a6628c9436\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-a1a0252c-1681-482f-859c-6bcda2c737ab\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line5\" id=\"SE-cda31c2c-d54e-4b57-9ce4-d585bea252c4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line5 se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-183467bb-f90f-4ba9-b9ef-cf8b7d09f81c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-16bfbfd7-3358-463a-b9f4-fa22dd002500\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ab553222-8fd1-49aa-8c97-d80a633f716a\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>디지털 소량이 가능한 스티커 종이</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-622f1a69-53d7-431b-b82d-e6814b832ebd\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b69c38ed-f95d-444c-ac9c-c737f7f35498\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-92829d2e-3d5d-4db1-83c3-97b50f714964\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-f6ed0d8f-9fef-4d7e-8553-6bff1a914b5d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">아트지 백색 90g (강접/초강접)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-f1f7b012-a7df-4502-9a3b-2cf6ae2b26a9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-1e8741d2-c8ae-4e11-aedd-540145d3708e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">아트지 백색 90g (리무버블)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-3fc2cecf-8a20-4901-a6ca-f5ebd93d53cf\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-2251e351-17fd-46e6-96bc-fd234d4f9e65\" style=\"color:#555555;\">모조지 백색 80g</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-5e0d5331-b060-46bd-8b4a-951b22fb6756\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-4116ed42-0717-40b3-8cf5-eb06962a3868\" style=\"color:#555555;\">크라프트지 57g</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line5\" id=\"SE-b87fcf9e-7169-45dc-9739-33e07e95f1cf\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line5 se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-797bb5de-f1a0-465c-ba90-b1311edb7950\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-2fe85ab9-035a-4c34-a4ed-87a277e897a1\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8327013a-3081-409c-9a7a-4dc1c4b3af0f\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>디지털 소량에 가능한 후공정</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-7dc5ad28-4e43-4b5b-bb68-2deab1d83d61\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-2d377c39-34f7-4648-a8ab-b4c483d7a206\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-7f6c920d-2510-4e54-8623-48e0310d5a55\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-eec21696-3738-473c-ab0f-9e2828293d62\" style=\"color:#555555;\">코팅 : 단면 무광/유광 라미네이팅</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-cb155894-555c-49ce-903c-775be9bc2669\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223888263832/008.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a10309c9-ef77-4bda-a4cc-24bbcd5f8db8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-bdd0bb60-e3f2-4281-b338-10bacad87559\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ea6b696b-4670-4a38-a97f-ff91f3fbc0dc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-20d2e553-741c-4935-991c-b13919af4ba9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-45417e8f-6b6b-4559-9dc7-310a68262028\" style=\"color:#555555;\">칼선 포함 이미지</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6f5d6f3d-1333-4993-9248-177c76219656\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223888263832/009.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-77555311-796b-4ffc-87b8-31a88b681e7a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\" style=\"max-width:617px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223888263832/010.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e6b0c381-f701-4583-87d9-50bc3d2b4595\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-e2cc00d4-7431-4a26-9487-d23cc9b86491\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e9a0359e-72ae-49a0-b168-83b5dd07c011\" style=\"color:#555555;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니은 고객님의 데이터를 그냥 점검 없이 진행하지는 않습니다. 거의 모든 고객님께서 각 회사에 맞는 접수나 주문방법에 대해 정확히 숙지하고 계시지는 못하고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-b4495413-9a95-4870-a760-11aec802efb6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-435e5c14-bce6-42a2-aa29-b624b75f460a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-4e6b0683-c843-4950-9a13-2e88cbedf94a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-39548abd-14a2-4345-aa20-98271b28e50d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이런 부분을 해소하고자 고객님의 데이터에 대한 검증작업을 반드시 시행하고 있습니다. 이런 과정을 거쳐야 사고 없이 진행할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-e386ac64-1911-4e96-8fcc-f11ba5eedfe7\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8b2c973d-8f1b-4309-a6b3-8a8bd06c6096\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-3890479e-79fa-4e7c-8d16-730354c1d91d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-df1ee8e5-5c81-44d0-aa0b-60ff9191c49f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-2ee45dcb-f3ab-4854-81e4-b09bd8f3d527\" style=\"\">이런 분은 꼭 전화 주세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6e2f9d16-951c-446b-9a4a-6d9651e0b307\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-e371f8fd-4fd9-4748-a010-0315cd9ece4a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-872b465c-4f43-4371-8838-ae588f6c00fb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">□ 급하게 소량의 스티커가 필요하신 분</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-2031f61a-7ed7-4e33-acb3-dadbf9ccc663\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-6d93768d-78c0-4ea8-af66-a6433d4e3547\" style=\"color:#555555;\">□ 본 작업 대량 생산 전에 디자인이나 상태를 확인하고 발주하고 싶으신 분</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-2223b341-8dab-4416-b7f9-6377a7d42f57\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-7c49ed2a-4851-4bbb-bd82-c756fcdf99a5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">□ 디자인 컨펌 단계에서 실제 인쇄물의 결과치와 비교하고 싶은 신 분</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-4365a2b1-b7b1-4cd9-8c07-f2d7f2615fe3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-386c2b77-d536-4fd8-81ab-2a21c4b47ce7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-53910440-e932-4d17-80ef-bd87a85f4fb8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
